1. CHARTERED STANDARDIZATION GUIDELINES:
We analyzed our entrepeneurial network best glocal rule-of-law procedures policies in both laic ethic development (2) and interfaith-inspiration basement (3) standards from the world most respectable institutions as directives for our project's code of conduct, license agreement, contributing guidelines, business contracts, museologic plan, creativity research, and entrepeneurial statute, as available on our website (https://ecumenic.github.io) and repository (https://github.com/ecumenic/project). 


